http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/tamil-nadu/Carom-tournament/article14619896.ece

Sports Development Authority of Tamil Nadu, Tiruchi, will conduct a district-level carom tournament for school students on September 6 at Anna Stadium here. The tournament will be conducted under two categories – for students of standards I to V and students of standards VI to XII. More details can be had by dialling 0431-2420685.